item.content:encoded:
Antistress – Relaxation Box is a casual online game. Choose a character and a tool for hitting and your task is to beat the blood bar to 0 in a limited time. Funny characters will beg you to slap them. It’s time to dominate the game and show them who is the king of face-slapping!
PC & MobileMouse click or tap to play

item.content:encoded:
Level Up Running is a running arcade game. You can collect boxing gloves and fight weak boxers on the platform to defeat the final boss at each level. If you meet a boxer who is stronger than yours, avoid to fight him but to avoid him.
On PC and MobileHold and swipe = move left and right
